<body>
  <h1>Registration Approved!</h1>
  
  <p>Dear <%= @registration.provider_name %>,</p>
  
  <p>Great news! Your registration for <strong><%= @registration.category.humanize %></strong> services has been approved.</p>
  
  <p>Your provider profile has been created and is now live on our platform. Families can now find and contact you for services.</p>
  
  <p>Next steps:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Complete your provider profile with additional details</li>
    <li>Add your service locations and hours</li>
    <li>Upload your logo and photos</li>
    <li>Set your availability and waitlist status</li>
  </ul>
  
  <p>If you have any questions or need assistance setting up your profile, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
  
  <p>Welcome to the Autism Services Locator family!</p>
  
  <p>Best regards,<br>
  The Autism Services Locator Team</p>
</body>
</html> 